WEBVTT

00:04.805 --> 00:06.273 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Good evening. I'm
Judy Woodruff.

00:06.306 --> 00:07.941 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And I'm Gwen Ifill.

00:07.975 --> 00:11.411 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: On the "NewsHour"
tonight,
we are on the ground in
Brussels. The city

00:11.445 --> 00:15.849 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
