and the most
effective way to fight terror.

00:15.883 --> 00:21.655 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: There is a mix
of fear and
resilience on the streets here
tonight, as

00:21.688 --> 00:25.492 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
