confronting extremism
in their midst.

00:25.525 --> 00:31.431 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Then: foreign policy
and the next
president, today, the Democrats.
Hillary Clinton

00:31.465 --> 00:34.468 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
