talk with
Bernie Sanders.

00:34.501 --> 00:38.505 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEN. BERNIE SANDERS (VT-I),
Presidential Candidate:
Can ISIS be destroyed? Of course
they can.

00:38.538 --> 00:43.377 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
