deportation
on July 14, 2015. Despite our
warnings that

04:41.848 --> 04:46.253 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
this person is a foreign
fighter, Belgium
could not establish any links
with terrorism.

04:46.286 --> 04:50.891 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Likewise,
French officials
have complained that Belgium
failed to conduct

04:50.924 --> 04:56.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
