areas after
the Paris attacks. French Prime
Minister Manuel

04:56.696 --> 05:00.934 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Valls called for greater
coordination today,
before traveling to Brussels.

05:00.967 --> 05:05.305 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MANUEL VALLS, French Prime
Minister (through
translator): We closed our eyes
everywhere

05:05.338 --> 05:10.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in Europe, including France, to
the progression
of extremist ideas,
neighborhoods which through

05:10.143 --> 05:15.282 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
a combination of drug
trafficking and radical
Islamism perverted youth. And
I'm not here

05:15.315 --> 05:18.451 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to lecture the Belgians, because
I'm sure
they're more than aware of this.

05:18.485 --> 05:22.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: There was also
word that
Secretary of State John Kerry
will travel

05:22.522 --> 05:26.993 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to Brussels on Friday to meet
with top Belgian
and European officials.

05:27.027 --> 05:33.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, tonight, European and Iraqi
intelligence
officials told the Associated
Press that ISIS

05:33.567 --> 05:37.737 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
