05:39.539 --> 05:44.678 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Malcolm,
given the threat
of these fighters, give us a
sense of the

05:44.711 --> 05:48.648 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
