traveled into
Belgium today.

05:48.682 --> 05:52.786 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Yes, I have
come from Lesbos
in Greece, and have traveled
through Athens

05:52.819 --> 05:54.588 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
