see the tension
in people's faces because they
just didn't

06:06.099 --> 06:07.968 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
know what was going on.

06:08.001 --> 06:14.307 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In Paris, the plane was met by
policemen checking
very assiduously everybody's
passports. And

06:14.341 --> 06:18.712 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
this is something that shouldn't
normally
happen within the Schengen free
travel zone.

06:18.745 --> 06:23.183 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
This is supposed to be
paper-free. But they
were checking everybody's
identities very

06:23.216 --> 06:24.918 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
closely.

06:24.951 --> 06:29.556 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Indeed, there were sniffer dogs
there. And
then driving into Belgium wasn't
a problem.

06:29.589 --> 06:33.393 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The border was wide open, but on
the other
side of the motorway, it was
very difficult

06:33.426 --> 06:38.298 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
