people that might
be involved in those attacks
yesterday.

06:43.470 --> 06:48.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And when I finally got into the
center of
Belgium, into Brussels this
morning -- this

06:48.141 --> 06:53.947 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
