everywhere, police
guards, and people checking --
being checked

06:59.920 --> 07:04.090 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as they went into the Eurostar
station, because
this is something that people
really are concerned

07:04.124 --> 07:07.894 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about, that, in order to get
into these places
now, you perhaps need to be
checked.

07:07.927 --> 07:11.498 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then there was a queue
outside. And these
are the sort of things that can
become soft

07:11.531 --> 07:17.003 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
