station and at
airports.

07:20.940 --> 07:25.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And just quickly,
Malcolm,
you reported on Turkey having
deported back

07:25.578 --> 07:33.186 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
