07:35.255 --> 07:39.359 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Well, this is
really embarrassing
for the Belgians, because the
Turkish president

07:39.392 --> 07:46.099 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
