08:10.090 --> 08:16.196 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Malcolm Brabant
reporting for
us tonight from Brussels, we
thank you.

08:16.229 --> 08:20.233 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
