to make Muslims feel
ghettoized."

09:21.828 --> 09:26.866 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Donald Trump was
off the campaign
trail today, but Ted Cruz was in
New York

09:26.900 --> 09:32.238 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
