48:58.202 --> 49:03.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A few days before the ceremony,
Abed called
and asked if I would serve as
his witness.

49:03.140 --> 49:07.545 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We had become close, but his
request was a
surprise. Yet, when I arrived at
