entirety of
the groom's party.

49:17.388 --> 49:22.092 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As the wedding started, there
were four of
us, the maid of honor, the
bride, Abed, and

49:22.126 --> 49:27.965 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
