a translation.

49:32.036 --> 49:36.707 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As Abed struggled to understand
his vows,
he glanced over to me now and
again, plaintively,

49:36.740 --> 49:40.878 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
