understand
either.

49:40.911 --> 49:45.082 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That a former American Marine
should serve
as the sole witness to a new
life embarked

49:45.115 --> 49:51.255 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
upon by a former Syrian activist
felt appropriate.
