us to craft
new lives from the wreckage.

49:56.360 --> 49:59.697 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Sitting next to my friend, it
didn't seem
to matter that he couldn't
understand the

49:59.730 --> 50:07.972 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
